description: |
  Testing standards and patterns for Vue.js components using Jest and Vue Test Utils with proper test coverage and quality.
globs:
  - tests/**/*.js
  - src/components/**/*.vue
  - src/store/**/*.js
  - src/services/**/*.js
alwaysApply: true
rules:
  # Testing Framework
  - Use Jest for unit testing
  - Use Vue Test Utils for component testing
  - Follow the established testing patterns
  - Implement proper test coverage

  # Component Testing
  - Test component props and events
  - Test component lifecycle methods
  - Test component state changes
  - Test component user interactions

  # Store Testing
  - Test store actions and mutations
  - Test store getters and state
  - Test store modules integration
  - Test store error handling

  # Service Testing
  - Test API service functions
  - Test error handling in services
  - Test service integration
  - Test service error responses

  # Test Organization
  - Co-locate tests with source files
  - Use descriptive test names
  - Follow the established test structure
  - Implement proper test setup and teardown

  # Test Quality
  - Write meaningful test assertions
  - Test edge cases and error conditions
  - Use proper test mocking
  - Follow the established testing patterns

